Package model

package model
This package contains the model components for the SC2002 Project. It includes classes that represent the core data structures and business logic of the application. The model package is responsible for managing the data and the rules of the business domain.

The classes in this package are responsible for:

  • Representing entities such as patients, doctors, appointments, and medical records
  • Defining relationships between these entities
  • Implementing business rules and logic
  • Providing methods to manipulate and access the data
